      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A smart starting Barolo because it shows rose, cherry, and Nebbiolo lift without feeling as forbidding as the sternest traditional bottles. It is especially useful for buyers who want real regional character but still plan to drink the bottle before it disappears into long-term storage.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Nebbiolo</p>
    </div>
