      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A reliable benchmark when you want polish without losing regional identity. This is often the bottle that helps buyers understand why Barolo can be powerful and precise at the same time, especially when you want one bottle that still respects tradition without punishing the drinker.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Nebbiolo</p>
    </div>
